OL,3,CLeaders pressed on guaranteeing
OL,4,CStormont stability
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's leaders have been
OL,7,Furged to give a commitment that they
OL,8,Fwill not collapse devolved government.
OL,10,FThe Stormont Executive and Assembly
OL,11,Fwas recently resurrected after a two-
OL,12,Fyear collapse following the
OL,13,Fresignation of former First Minister
OL,14,FPaul Givan over his DUP party's
OL,15,Fopposition to the Northern Ireland
OL,16,FProtocol.
OL,18,FPrior to that, Sinn Fein collapsed
OL,19,Fdevolved government for almost three
OL,20,Fyears from 2017 to 2020.
