OL,3,CLeaders pressed on guaranteeing
OL,4,CStormont stability
OL,6,FHe added: "Such a commitment is, I
OL,7,Fbelieve, strongly in the public
OL,8,Finterest.
OL,10,F"Faith in our democratic institutions
OL,11,Fhas been shattered by the failure to
OL,12,Fgovern."
OL,14,FMr O'Toole added: "Many believed that
OL,15,Fthe most recent collapse of the
OL,16,Fdemocratic institutions would be the
OL,17,Ffinal straw.
