OL,6,F"I firmly believe that a further
OL,7,Ffailure of power sharing would put
OL,8,Fdevolution beyond repair in the minds
OL,9,Fof most.
OL,11,F"A guarantee that you and your party
OL,12,Fwill not bring down the Executive for
OL,13,Fthe rest of this mandate would go some
OL,14,Fway to restoring lost confidence in
OL,15,Four institutions."
